public class HibernateGeneralGenericDao

A Hibernate (http://hibernate.org/) based implementation of GeneralGenericDao which can be extended to add more specialized DAO methods.

See the overview for installation/usage tips.

Author:
Aaron Zeckoski (aaronz@vt.edu)
